# 🩺 HealthCard

A Django-based healthcare web application that helps manage and regulate medicine sales and user health records.

---

## 🌟 Features

- 🧾 Digital health card system
- 🔒 User authentication (login/register)
- 🏥 Add and view patient details
- 💊 Medicine history tracking
- 📊 Admin dashboard for monitoring
- 🌐 Built with Django + SQLite

---

## 🚀 How to Run

```bash
# Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/YOUR-USERNAME/HealthCard.git
cd HealthCard

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv env
env\Scripts\activate  # On Windows

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# Run migrations
python manage.py migrate

# Start the server
python manage.py runserver

